{
  "texts": [
    "I. INTRODUCTIONIn today's world, cybersecurity has become increasingly important due to the rapid expansion of digital platforms and the growing complexity of cyber threats.",
    "Its significance lies in protecting against these threats, preserving individual privacy, securing businesses, preventing financial losses, and maintaining public security.",
    "A notable progress in the field of cybersecurity is the rise of Artificial Intelligence (AI) as a transformative force.",
    "AI offers robust results that surpass traditional security systems.",
    "AI's capabilities include analyzing large datasets, adapting to new information, and accurately predicting potential threats."
  ]
}